<style>
  div#all {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 0 100px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  p {
    font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 24px;
    text-align: justify;
    color: #000000
  }

  a {
    font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 800;
    background-color: rgb(0, 132, 62);
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    align-self: center;
    line-height: 24px;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin: 20px 0;
  }

  svg {
    margin: 20px 0;
    align-self: center;
  }

  a:hover {
    background-color: rgb(1, 90, 43);
    cursor: pointer;
  }

</style>

<div id="all">

  <p>Dear <%= @user.full_name %>,</p>
  
  <p>Welcome to Wroom! We're thrilled to have you join our growing community of AI writers. To get started on your writing journey, we kindly ask you to verify your email address by clicking the link below:</p>
  
  <%= link_to 'Confirm my account', confirmation_url(@resource, confirmation_token: @token) %>
  
  <p>Once verified, you will be ready to supercharge your writing process with Wroom!</p>
  
  <p>If you encounter any issues or have any questions, our support team is here to assist you. Reach out to us at info@wroom.ai or join the Wroom Discord community, and we'll be happy to help!</p>
  
  <p>Happy writing!</p>
  
  <p>Best regards,</p>
  
  <p>The Wroom Team</p>
</div>